{"id": 3049, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都习惯了生活中的哪些东西迭代得特别快？", "description": "更重要的是，我们是从啥时候起，逐渐接受“这些事物的寿命就是很短”这件事儿的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ AlisaRut）", "record_count": 6341, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191105004558jts7o0vQIxGKAJEB.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6015, "title": "你都习惯了生活中的哪些东西迭代得特别快？", "content": "现如今你都习惯了哪些东西迭代得特别快？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349133, "content": "手机之类电子产品，一年换一台都是正常操作", "image": "img/option/option/20191105001015bFr4pyLamKUXzA1V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349134, "content": "衣服/时尚，下个季度打开衣橱就会觉得“我都买了啥”", "image": "img/option/option/20191104224914wa1DtMYnEk4HBgZR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349135, "content": "热点/流行语，稍微没注意就会完全跟流行脱节", "image": "img/option/option/20191105001253f6uPZyVgmMrpvwGK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349136, "content": "“风口”创业产品，出现跟消失的速度几乎一样快", "image": "img/option/option/20191105001320t2P0J8fK7lkuLXTw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349137, "content": "职场，超过 35 岁就会被反复暗示“年纪大了”", "image": "img/option/option/20191105005026Z6TgM54fPuDKlBqU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349138, "content": "信息/知识，过个一两年再看很多都“过时”了", "image": "img/option/option/20191105002621b86dpyUu1mPaiXjc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349139, "content": "社会关系，换一个环境/阵地差不多就得换一批朋友", "image": "img/option/option/20191105002341kTXexgE812vIJtLV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349140, "content": "生活方式，从线下到“万物皆可线上”其实也就几年时间", "image": "img/option/option/20191105001850pCQsaoDvP2ORJiAt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}